snippet.title: Grapple Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is Grapple! It's a 3D puzzle platformer where you climb up walls, walk on ceilings, and can swing on just about anything. Travel through complex obstacle courses in space to try and get to the black hole. 

We're releasing soon, so keep an eye out!

Follow us on twitter @TuesdaySociety
